                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9574" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1435</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1629 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智扬帆，云旅逐梦——云创科技数据资产化之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sailing with Digital Intelligence, Pursuing Dreams in Cloud Travel - The Journey of Data Assetization with Cloud Innovation Technology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李永红，崔家超，赵亚楠，赵佳瑶，肖明刚，许心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西安邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西云创网络科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数据资产化；数据资源；数据资产入表；文化和旅游产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Data Assetization; Data Resources; Data Asset Capitalization; Cultural and Tourism Industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024年，陕西云创科技股份有限公司通过将“文旅产业运营数据集”作为数据资产入表，成功获得交通银行陕西省分行500万元融资授信，实现了数据资源到资产的全流通闭环。公司以“技术引领，运营赋能”为核心战略，构建了智旅建设、智旅运营和数智营销三大核心板块，为文旅产业链提供全方位数字解决方案。在此基础上，云创科技依据国家标准建立数据管理体系，精细化管理数据资产，确保数据的高质量与合规性。财务团队采用“数据资产入表五步法”，结合北京国际大数据交易所在数据确权方面的专业支持，以成本法对数据资产进行计量并完成入表操作。尽管面临数据交易市场不活跃和相关政策不完善的挑战，云创科技积极探索市场策略，加强政策沟通，推动数据资产的市场化应用。本案例旨在帮助学员理解数据资产的定义及其与数据资源的区别，掌握数据资产确认和计量与传统资产的差异，熟悉数据资产入表的具体步骤及其为企业带来的收益和问题，并通过对云创科技战略规划的分析，引导学员思考数据资产的智能化管理及未来应用领域的拓展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2024, Shaanxi Cloud Innovation Technology Co., Ltd. successfully obtained a 5 million yuan financing credit from Bank of Communications, Shaanxi Branch, by capitalizing its &quot;Cultural and Tourism Industry Operation Dataset&quot; as a data asset, thus achieving a full circulation loop from data resources to data assets. Adhering to the core strategy of &quot;technology leadership and operational empowerment,&quot; the company has established three core business segments: Intelligent Tourism Construction, Intelligent Tourism Operation, and Digital Marketing. These segments provide comprehensive digital solutions for the cultural and tourism industry chain. Based on this foundation, Cloud Innovation Technology has developed a data management system in accordance with national standards, meticulously managing data assets to ensure their high quality and compliance. The finance team adopted the &quot;Five-Step Method for Data Asset Capitalization&quot; and collaborated with the Beijing International Big Data Exchange for data entitlement, using the cost approach to measure the value of data assets and complete their capitalization. Despite challenges such as an inactive data trading market and imperfect relevant policies, the company actively explores market strategies, strengthens policy communication, and promotes the market-oriented application of data assets. This case aims to help students understand the definition of data assets and their distinction from data resources, grasp the differences between the confirmation and measurement of data assets and traditional assets, become familiar with the specific steps of data asset capitalization and the benefits and issues it brings to enterprises, and guide students to think about the intelligent management of data assets and their future application fields through an analysis of Cloud Innovation Technology&#39;s strategic planning.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">会计管理活动理论；数据资产概念；数据资产确认与计量；数据资产入表步骤；数据资产应用；数据资产管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-04</td>
                            </tr>
